name: Cargolux Airlines International Boeing 747-8R7F Beautiful Takeoff from Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everyone, this is a Cargolux Airlines International Boeing 747-8F departing Calgary bound for Luxembourg. This bird was very late because at the time I filmed it, it was already 1:00 PM, when these normally come in 12 hours earlier! Sorry for all the haze in the video too. I hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
